snippet.textDisplay:
To think that a country with such great taste and exceptional talent  in all art forms was once in oneness with us. 
What this art makes us feel, we feel as humans and not as Indians or Pakistanis. Only if we understood that there's no 'I' but only 'We'.
Its sad what happened, how we got separated. And we still remain...Always hoping for better times...
